data.description: This is Short Sale subject to lender approval! This charming home is now available for the incredible price of $249,700.  Centrally located in Brawley! This delightful 2 bedroom/2bath home offers the added flexibility of easily converting the den or office space into that of a third bedroom if desired.   Situated across the street from Barbara Worth Middle School, it provides easy access for families with children. The property boasts an RV concrete slab, allowing for convenient parking and storage options. With the potential for a third bedroom, this home offers flexibility and room to grow. Its accessible layout ensures ease of movement throughout the house. Call your favorite realtor to schedule a showing, this won't last!
